  "notes": "Live Shopify evidence that draft-order line items with variantId ignore custom-only input fields such as title, sku, originalUnitPrice, taxable, and requiresShipping. The capture uses a disposable product variant with known catalog values, supplies bogus custom-only values to draftOrderCreate and draftOrderCalculate, and asserts Shopify returns catalog-derived line-item values."
